<b>St.James English Medium Convent School</b> is a minority community institution managed  by the Sister of St.James Convent, Azhikode. We admit students of all communities irrespective of  caste or creed, rich or poor.</br></br>This intention of this institution is to impart wisdom through knowledge, love, service, courage and development. This means the total development of whole person.</br></br>We strive to make the student spiritually oriented, morally upright emotionally mature, intellectually well-informed, academically progressive, socially aware, genuinely compassionate, partriotic, economically self reliant and eco-friendly.</br></br>     